<paragraph blockId="12.[151,1436,626,1092]" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,320,986,1012]" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">Remarks.</emphasis>
I was unable to obtain females of this species for examination. 
<bibRefCitation author="Casagrande" box="[1099,1324,986,1012]" pageId="12" pageNumber="16" refString="Casagrande, M. M. (2004) Brassolini. p. 201 - 205. In: J. B. Heppner (ed.). Atlas of Neotropical Lepidoptera. Part 4 A Checklist (ed. by G. Lamas). Association of Tropical Lepidoptera / Scientific publishers, Gainesville. 439 p." type="book chapter" year="2004">
Casagrande (
<number box="[1254,1316,986,1012]" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" value="2004.0">2004</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
